## ⴰⵙⵉⵏⴰⵡⴰⵙ (amazigh):

Agan amezwaru d AGPL-3.0.
- Tzemreḍ ad tesqedceḍ, ad tbedleḍ, ad tesqedceḍ s tikkelt-nniḍen, ad tkemmeḍ s uselkim (SaaS, cloud, API).
- Yella ad tkemmeḍ kra n usnifel d AGPL-3.0.
- Imeslayen d imellalen n usnifel, yella ad ilin d AGPL-3.0.
- Sefk tawuri n tmedyazt, RGPD, tazwart, tɣellist.

