## English summary:

This project is licensed under AGPL-3.0.
- You may use, modify, distribute, host, and contribute to the code, including SaaS/cloud/API.
- Any modification or network use must be published under AGPL-3.0.
- Contributions remain property of their authors, but must be AGPL-3.0 compatible.
- Digital sovereignty, GDPR, accessibility, and security must be respected.

